FT  27 JUN 94 / Observer: Talent spotted
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
One more tale to add to the Queens Moat Houses' collection.
When the bankers to the heavily-indebted hotel group were scrabbling around
last year wondering what to do as deadlines approached, they decided in
desperation to call in an accountancy firm specialising in corporate
breakdowns.
